<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Chirpy - Home</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to Chirpy!</h1>
    
    <p>
        <a href="/">Home</a> | 
        <a href="/register/">Register</a> | 
        <a href="/login/">Login</a> | 
        <a href="/logout/">Logout</a>
        <a href="/listusers/">List All Users</a>
        <a href="/listcookies/">View Cookies</a>
    </p>

    <p>
        Hello. It is now ${date}. Sadly, Chirpy doesn't do much currently. But you'll fix that! (Yay!)
    </p>

    <p>
        To get started:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/register/">Create an account</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login/">Login to your account</a></li>
        <li><a href="/listusers/">See all registered users</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Here's a list of random numbers:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <#list randvector as randNum>
            <li>${randNum}</li>
        </#list>
    </ul>
</body>
</html>